<html>
  <head>
    <title>Minerva Training Schedule Update</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <table
      align="center"
      border="0"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      width="600"
    >
      {{> emailHeader }}
      <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#ffffff" style="padding: 40px 30px 40px 30px;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
            <tr>
              <td
                style="color: #555555; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px;"
              >
                Minerva Training Schedule Update
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style="padding: 20px 0 30px 0; color: #555555; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;"
              >
                Dear
                {{username}},
                <br /><br />
                We would like to inform you about an update to the course
                schedule for the
                {{courseName}}. Please take note of the following changes:
                <br /><br />
                <strong>Old Schedule:</strong>
                <ul>
                  <li>Date: {{oldDate}}</li>
                  <li>Time: {{oldTime}}</li>
                  <li>Location: {{oldLocation}}</li>
                </ul>
                <strong>New Schedule:</strong>
                <ul>
                  <li>Date: {{newDate}}</li>
                  <li>Time: {{newTime}}</li>
                  <li>Location: {{newLocation}}</li>
                </ul>
                We apologize for any inconvenience caused by this change. We
                have made the necessary adjustments to ensure a smooth
                continuation of the training program.
                <br /><br />
                If you have any questions or concerns regarding the updated
                schedule, please feel free to contact our training coordinator,
                {{coordinatorName}}, at
                {{coordinatorEmail}}
                or
                {{coordinatorPhone}}. They will be happy to assist you.
                <br /><br />
                We appreciate your understanding and flexibility regarding this
                schedule update. Thank you for your participation in the
                training program.
                <br /><br />
                Best regards,
                <br />
                The Minerva Support Team
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
      {{> emailFooter }}
    </table>
  </body>
</html>